    Welcome to Our Community

    Welcome to our official website!

    I hope you find it useful in locating our courses, services, and other information about us.

    ​

    This is your gateway to Mombasa Aviation Training Institute. Here you will meet students and staff, make quick inquiries about us and fill out request forms for any of our services.

     

    Our focus here is to educate the whole person and find opportunities for our students to experience the professional life in line with our motto “Profession is Power”.

    ​

    Our future direction is reflected in our pursuit of excellent training where we emphasize on the intellectual, social, physical and spiritual dimensions of life. I welcome you to expand the borders of your mind with us.

    ​

    Mombasa Aviation Training Institute is a world-class tertiary institution which offers a wide range of courses in aviation studies, hospitality & tourism, business studies, freight forwarding, media studies and so on.

    ​

    All these courses have been packaged to ensure that our graduates will suit the demands of the aviation and other related industries. 

    ​

    MATI was registered by the Ministry of Higher Education, Science & Technology in the year 2008 to offer technical, vocational and entrepreneurial skills to majority of people who demand tertiary education - mostly the youth after completing their O' level studies.

    ​

    Some of our clients are also people in employment who come for further studies in specific areas related to the work they do.

    Aeronautical engineering

    ​

    This course deals with the mechanical, electrical and electronic principles of the parts of the aircraft including its engines, wings and interior communication systems which the pilot uses to control the aircraft movement.
